IN RE AALANAH M. Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided October 24, 2018

The petition by the respondent father for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court (AC 42070) is dismissed without prejudice to filing a motion for permission to file a late appeal with the Appellate Court on or before November 5, 2018.

D'AURIA and MULLINS, Js., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.
